```python
def get_note(pitch):
    notes = {
        440: "A",
        466.16: "A#",
        493.88: "B",
        523.25: "C",
        554.37: "C#",
        587.33: "D",
        622.25: "D#",
        659.25: "E",
        698.46: "F",
        739.99: "F#",
        783.99: "G",
        830.61: "G#"
    }
    # Normalize the pitch to the nearest note in the dictionary
    while pitch not in notes:
        if pitch > 830.61:
            pitch /= 2
        else:
            pitch *= 2
    return notes[pitch]
```
